Description.SourceString: This Nevish vessel excels in punching holes in the hulls of the Colonial fleet. Armed with Moray Torpedos and state-of-the-art sonar technology, the Nakki is a silent killer. Famously, three Nakkis crept behind a Colonial fleet at night and picked them apart one by one, leading to Prefect Evander to call a retreat. Their “Legion” was not at all prepared to be assaulted from under the waves.
